tip.text: Really good pho. Small portion but that means you can do seconds! For sure add in condiments - those orange chili and pink paste are hot
Amazing little place! #1 must have - very peppery and flavorful. #5 also great!

Soooo delicious that we ordered seconds while still having the first. I loved the pate one. Staff are also really friendly. There is a sweet little girl practising English while serving. Free iced tea
Egg? Coffee? Um...yeah!!! That sweetness and creaminess...it's delish beyond my imagination!!! Love love love. Already decided to return for a cold one later today
The seafood noodles and spring rolls (total 540k). A little more pricey than a typical street stall due to its popularity and seafood as main ingredient.
Matcha cupcake was sooo good! Rich matcha taste in both cake and icing.
